import Vue from 'vue'
import Router from 'vue-router'


import login from './components/login'


Vue.use(Router)


const routes = [
    { path: '/login', component: login },
]


const router = new Router({
    routes,
    linkActiveClass: 'router-link-active'
})

export default router
